---
title: Double Caribbean Chicken & Creamy Cos Salad with Charred Pineapple Salsa
description: Fire up the grill for this Caribbean-inspired feast! Juicy, spice-rubbed chicken is flame-kissed to perfection, paired with
a refreshing creamy cos lettuce salad. A sweet, smokey charred pineapple salsa adds a tropical twist, balancing the heat with bursts of caramelised goodness. This BBQ delight brings island vibes to your plate with every bite!
